&lt;li&gt;To keep $\sigma_1$ in pristine condition while creating create $\sigma_2$ and $\sigma_3$&lt;br&gt;:::info 方法：&lt;br&gt;persistent BST&lt;br&gt;:::&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
